# Extend MapConfig

When changing map configuration contracts:

- Start with `.claude/skills/extend-map-config/SKILL.md`.
- Treat `packages/map-ui-lib/src/schemas/config.ts` as the source of truth.
- Propagate changes through hydration, stores, URL sync, and consuming UI.
- Validate compatibility with existing `config.json` usage patterns.

